During the operation, an ear, nose and throat specialist - who was not certified by the clinic, as required by law - performed a biopsy on the star's vocal cords.

The medic was described by the source as Joan's personal ENT specialist, who is reported to be Dr Korovin.   

According to CNN, Dr Korovin also allegedly snapped a selfie with Rivers while the star was under anesthesia.

 

 

 

 

  

 

 

